Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:09.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:20.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:39.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:46.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:53.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.92,0:00:59.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:06.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.80,0:01:14.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.11,0:01:20.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:27.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:09.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, more... More powerful, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:18.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, don't look! You can't\Nkill them if you see their eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:41.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:47.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:15.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wounds and Pain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:25.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Alty. Chase those birds. Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:28.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're on duty right now, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:32.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,So what? We won't\Nrun into the enemy here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:35.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,You'll just miss out\Nif you're so wound up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:38.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you're\Nright about that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:45.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,They've been flying by us awhile.\NI wonder where they're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:49.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,They can't fly forever. They'll rest\Ntheir wings when they're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:53.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,They've got to eat\Nwhen they get hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:04:00.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are they doing? We're on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:11.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Things seem pretty\Nmellow these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:13.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:18.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,We finally returned to duty too.\NWe seem to have lost our edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:21.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,And Aer never\Nvolunteers to fly anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:30.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,How's Sibylla Aurea\Ndoing these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:33.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,The same, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you concerned?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:36.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:40.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it's like we've been left hanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:43.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,It seems like the others are\Nstarting to accept her being gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:50.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,This means we can never go back\Nto the old Chor Tempest, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:54.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:57.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm keeping\Nan eye on you, Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:10.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone,\Nwe're heading for the pool now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:11.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:12.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not.\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:14.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're still young, so your endurance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:16.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're still young, so your endurance...\NI'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:19.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone! Hey, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:23.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um, why don't we all take lunch first?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:39.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter,\NSibylla Paraietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is Sibylla Aurea's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm still repairing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:48.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,We had to rebuild\Nsome things from scratch...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:52.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,...so I had a hard time\Ngetting all the components.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:58.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your wounds haven't healed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,You haven't flown in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril! Hey, Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:27.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,You've been cooped up long enough.\NGet back on duty already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:34.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest just gets lame missions\Nbecause you won't come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:37.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't take much more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:40.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is no place for us to be flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you listening, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:57.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,You stubborn mule!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:16.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really, what a childish thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:29.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm in no position to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:44.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. There was\Nno need for you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:47.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, I really didn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:50.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really, what are\Nwe going to do with Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:54.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's troubling you, right?\NShall I make her stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:08:00.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm sure\Nit's not going to be pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:12.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril... Don't you think\Nit's time you made things clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Made what clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:17.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Made what clear?\NEither way, we can't go on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:20.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Won't you come back to the chor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:27.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you decide to go to the Spring,\Nthen this time I'll accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:28.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:34.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm still unsure myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:37.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,About going to the Spring...\Nand about flying Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:39.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't decide yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:41.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:43.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm fully aware that it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:50.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I feel that no matter which choice\NI make, it would be a betrayal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:52.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Betrayal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the feeling I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean Amuria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:14.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril... I've spent my life by your\Nside ever since we were children.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've always walked\Nthe same path as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:20.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I can say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:24.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your place is in a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:30.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even if that means\Nyou'll have to betray Amuria...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me as if you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:38.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not as simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:03.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:06.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's overwhelmed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:11.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,And you've been so worried\Nabout her, Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:26.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I don't see why she doesn't\Ntry to understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:29.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't like the way Neviril's acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:32.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:33.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:36.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nshe's just being childish, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:40.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:42.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then what's up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:56.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure, losing Amuria\Nwas a big blow to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:59.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but she's not\Nthe only one who misses her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:04.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Keeping herself holed up is really\Ncausing trouble for the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:05.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:12.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I was out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:14.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:17.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened to your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:19.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was cleaning something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:23.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can't just leave them like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know! Could you wait a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:36.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see... My nails are starting to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:40.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aren't they? You've got such beautiful\Nfingers, so take care of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:43.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,...or Tempus Spatium will scold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,You enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:52.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm getting to take care of you, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:56.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,And touch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:58.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think she's just lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:09.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,We probably all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:11.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of us on this ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:16.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Lonely, probably... That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:26.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:30.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:34.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you lonely too, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:38.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do I look that bad to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:40.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:44.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm asking because I'm lonely too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:59.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's hot in here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:02.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then why don't\Nwe go where it's cooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:13.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,No change in the princess yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:15.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:18.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,It reminds me of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like a certain someone, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:28.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not uncommon for a sibylla\Nto question her flight duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:33.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was the one who offered\Nyou a helping hand then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:36.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I haven't forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:38.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:39.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pow-pow-pow-pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:42.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:44.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vroom! Blam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:47.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pow-pow-pow-pow!\NI see some more coming at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:49.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Blam! Pow-pow-pow-pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:54.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared of that lame attack!\NLet's see you hit us if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vroom! Pow-pow-pow-pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:00.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey! Para-sama!\NEnemy to your right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:03.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Strafe them with\Nthe machine gun! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:04.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pow-pow-pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:08.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow, Para-sama! 100 of 100!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pow-pow-pow! Pow-pow-pow-pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:14.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Another group of enemies\Nbeyond the clouds! Ray Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:22.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:26.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:29.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's do a Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:49.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Strange... We always do that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:08.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh! We've got to turn it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:33.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister Kaim...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was always by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:11.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd decided to stay by her side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:17.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,And before I knew it, being near\Nher had become a natural thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:30.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,How arrogant of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:35.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thinking I was the only\None she could ever lean on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:39.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought that it was obvious...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:53.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,In that moment,\NI wasn't the only one who felt pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:59.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that the reason why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:11.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's not do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:12.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's not do this.\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:15.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're still a child, Kaim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? I'm not a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:18.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:19.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,You are.\NI'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:22.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're all children.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:27.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why we try to heal our wounds\Nbut end up creating new wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:32.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:34.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good night, Kaim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:41.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:46.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Jeez, why can't you\Nsee how I feel, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:00.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:03.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril! Just listen to me\Nfor a second, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:05.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:07.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:16.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now that it's come to this, I'll drag\Nyou out if it's the last thing I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:18.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:21.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, I'd like to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:30.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like we're\Nabout to do any talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:36.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,The maju pool can\Nbe used for this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:43.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,So how did I end up\Nhaving to face you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:49.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:05.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,The reason Neviril refuses to decide\Nisn't just because of Amuria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:12.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was also out of\Nrespect for my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:18.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, I'm sorry.\NI didn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:23.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,But just let me say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:27.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't feel as though\Nyou've betrayed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:35.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I appreciate how\Nconsiderate you're being.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:37.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:40.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:47.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I'll put my hopes on\None who can surpass Amuria!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:58.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:02.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:03.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:11.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're open!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:12.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:23.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:40.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer! Go and pair up with Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.77,0:21:46.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:54.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Floe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:56.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.45,0:21:58.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,So what happens next?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:00.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:04.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,The birds who rest their wings...\NYou said they couldn't fly forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:07.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,They'll fly again of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.56,0:22:08.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,They will?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:13.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right. Because birds\Nwere born to fly in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:16.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,To fly in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,If she's resting her wings, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.68,0:22:30.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,But a bird who can't fly\Nbecause she's been wounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:33.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,...has no hope of survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.03,0:22:47.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:51.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:58.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:06.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:19.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.57,0:23:24.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.74,0:23:28.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.74,0:23:32.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.71,0:23:38.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.62,0:23:44.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.16,0:23:47.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.63,0:23:53.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.27,0:23:59.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:05.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:06.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued\NIn order to sign a peace treaty...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.45,0:24:07.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,In order to sign a peace treaty...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.75,0:24:13.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,...delegations from the highlands and\Nthe Arcus Prima are about to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.52,0:24:15.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.29,0:24:16.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Over International Waters\NNext time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.46,0:24:19.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Over International Waters\NOver International Waters.
